text: VietachetaGorochov AV (1992). In Gorochov & Korotiaev [Ed.]. News of Systematics and Faunistics of Vietnam Insects Part 2. Trudy Zool. Inst., Akad. Nauk SSSR, Leningrad 240: 3. is a genus of crickets in the family Gryllidae and tribe Gryllini. Species can be found in southern China and Vietnam.Orthoptera Species File (Version 5.0/5.0: retrieved 26 August 2019) == Species == Vietacheta includes the following species: *Vietacheta aquila Gorochov, 1992 *Vietacheta fumea Gorochov, 1992 *Vietacheta harpophylla Ma, Liu & Xu, 2015 *Vietacheta picea Gorochov, 1992 \- type species == References == == External links== * Category:Ensifera genera Category:Gryllinae Category:Orthoptera of Indo-China
